org.block.plugin.launch.meta

Annotation Type Dependent


  • public @interface Dependent
    The information of if the loading plugin required another plugin to load before hand. If A dependent is specified, then that depending plugin will be loaded first. This class can also be used in some events whereby the event will be fired to the depending plugin first and then this plugin

      • canLoadWithout

        public abstract boolean canLoadWithout
        Checks if this plugin can be loaded without the depending plugin. If the plugin requires this specified plugin for extra features, however does not need the dependent to make this plugin work, then specify this to be true
        Returns:
        If this plugin can load without the dependent plugin
